          "id": "nintendo-world-championships-nes-edition-announced-for-switc",
          "title": "**Nintendo World Championships: NES Edition** announced for Switch with 'over 150 challenges from 13 NES games'",
          "body": null,
          "url": "https://www.eurogamer.net/nintendo-world-championships-nes-edition-announced-for-switch-with-over-150-challenges-from-13-nes-games",
          "source": {
            "name": "Eurogamer",
            "domain": "eurogamer.net"
          },
          "metadata": {
            "story_type": "confirmed",
            "importance": "normal"
          },
          "bullets": [
            "Specifically concerned with speedrunning the game features 150 \"byte-sized\" challenges that can be tackled across several modes across 13 games:",
            "Balloon Fight",
            "Donkey Kong",
            "Excitebike",
            "Ice Climber",
            "Kid Icarus",
            "Kirby’s Adventure",
            "Metroid",
            "Super Mario Bros.",
            "Super Mario Bros. 2",
            "Super Mario Bros. 3",
            "Super Mario Bros. The Lost Levels",
            "The Legend of Zelda",
            "Zelda 2: The Adventure of Link",
            "Will be available digitally for £24.99 via Switch's eShop on 18th July, and a £49.99 physical Deluxe Set releases at the same time."
          ]
        },
